{"toc": "<ul>\n<li><a class=\"reference internal\" href=\"#\">Administrator Manual</a><ul>\n<li><a class=\"reference internal\" href=\"#requirements\">Requirements</a></li>\n<li><a class=\"reference internal\" href=\"#installation\">Installation</a></li>\n<li><a class=\"reference internal\" href=\"#insert-plugin\">Insert plugin</a><ul>\n<li><a class=\"reference internal\" href=\"#blog\">Blog</a></li>\n<li><a class=\"reference internal\" href=\"#categories\">Categories</a></li>\n<li><a class=\"reference internal\" href=\"#archive\">Archive</a></li>\n<li><a class=\"reference internal\" href=\"#keywords\">Keywords</a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n", "metatags": "", "next": {"link": "../../Configuration/Index/", "title": "Configuration Reference"}, "body": "<div class=\"section\" id=\"administrator-manual\">\n<span id=\"admin-manual\"></span><h1>Administrator Manual<a class=\"headerlink\" href=\"#administrator-manual\" title=\"Permalink to this headline\">\u00b6</a></h1>\n<p>Target group: <strong>Administrators</strong></p>\n<div class=\"contents local topic\" id=\"within-this-page\">\n<p class=\"topic-title first\">Within this page</p>\n<ul class=\"simple\">\n<li><a class=\"reference internal\" href=\"#requirements\" id=\"id2\">Requirements</a></li>\n<li><a class=\"reference internal\" href=\"#installation\" id=\"id3\">Installation</a></li>\n<li><a class=\"reference internal\" href=\"#insert-plugin\" id=\"id4\">Insert plugin</a><ul>\n<li><a class=\"reference internal\" href=\"#blog\" id=\"id5\">Blog</a></li>\n<li><a class=\"reference internal\" href=\"#categories\" id=\"id6\">Categories</a></li>\n<li><a class=\"reference internal\" href=\"#archive\" id=\"id7\">Archive</a></li>\n<li><a class=\"reference internal\" href=\"#keywords\" id=\"id8\">Keywords</a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n<div class=\"section\" id=\"requirements\">\n<h2><a class=\"toc-backref\" href=\"#id2\">Requirements</a><a class=\"headerlink\" href=\"#requirements\" title=\"Permalink to this headline\">\u00b6</a></h2>\n<div class=\"admonition caution\">\n<p class=\"first admonition-title\">Caution</p>\n<p class=\"last\">You must load the jQuery JavaScript framework yourself as the frontend plugin utilizes functions that depend on jQuery.</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"section\" id=\"installation\">\n<h2><a class=\"toc-backref\" href=\"#id3\">Installation</a><a class=\"headerlink\" href=\"#installation\" title=\"Permalink to this headline\">\u00b6</a></h2>\n<ol class=\"arabic simple\">\n<li>Download and install the extension via the extension manager (extKey: datec_blog).</li>\n<li>Add one storage folder for comments and comment creators, note down the page id (PID) of this folder.</li>\n<li>Check the Configuration section of this manual for the required configuration and follow the steps there.</li>\n<li>Insert the main plugin and optional ones as described below.</li>\n</ol>\n</div>\n<div class=\"section\" id=\"insert-plugin\">\n<h2><a class=\"toc-backref\" href=\"#id4\">Insert plugin</a><a class=\"headerlink\" href=\"#insert-plugin\" title=\"Permalink to this headline\">\u00b6</a></h2>\n<ol class=\"arabic simple\">\n<li>Insert a content element, choose &#8220;Plugins&#8221; -&gt; &#8220;General Plugin&#8221;</li>\n</ol>\n<div class=\"figure\">\n<a class=\"reference internal image-reference\" href=\"../../_images/ExtensionManager.png\"><img alt=\"insert plugin\" src=\"../../_images/ExtensionManager.png\" style=\"width: 652px;\" /></a>\n</div>\n<ol class=\"arabic simple\" start=\"2\">\n<li>Choose one of the display forms to setup your blog.</li>\n</ol>\n<div class=\"figure\" id=\"id1\">\n<a class=\"reference internal image-reference\" href=\"../../_images/ExtensionManager.png\"><img alt=\"modules\" src=\"../../_images/ExtensionManager.png\" style=\"width: 539px;\" /></a>\n<p class=\"caption\"><span class=\"caption-text\">Modules</span><a class=\"headerlink\" href=\"#id1\" title=\"Permalink to this image\">\u00b6</a></p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"section\" id=\"blog\">\n<h3><a class=\"toc-backref\" href=\"#id5\">Blog</a><a class=\"headerlink\" href=\"#blog\" title=\"Permalink to this headline\">\u00b6</a></h3>\n<p>Displays a the bloglist with filter and single view of posts with comments. This Plugin is required.</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"section\" id=\"categories\">\n<h3><a class=\"toc-backref\" href=\"#id6\">Categories</a><a class=\"headerlink\" href=\"#categories\" title=\"Permalink to this headline\">\u00b6</a></h3>\n<p>Displays Categories as a tree, clickable for the filter.</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"section\" id=\"archive\">\n<h3><a class=\"toc-backref\" href=\"#id7\">Archive</a><a class=\"headerlink\" href=\"#archive\" title=\"Permalink to this headline\">\u00b6</a></h3>\n<p>Generates an Archive from all Blogposts, displayed as tree of year - month - day, clickable for the filter.</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"section\" id=\"keywords\">\n<h3><a class=\"toc-backref\" href=\"#id8\">Keywords</a><a class=\"headerlink\" href=\"#keywords\" title=\"Permalink to this headline\">\u00b6</a></h3>\n<p>Displays Keywords as cloud or list, depending on your plugin TypoScript configuration, clickable for the filter.</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n", "parents": [], "rellinks": [["genindex", "General Index", "I", "index"], ["Configuration/Index", "Configuration Reference", "N", "next"], ["UsersManual/Index", "Users manual", "P", "previous"]], "title": "Administrator Manual", "meta": {}, "customsidebar": null, "sidebars": null, "current_page_name": "AdministratorManual/Index", "display_toc": true, "sourcename": "AdministratorManual/Index.txt", "prev": {"link": "../../UsersManual/Index/", "title": "Users manual"}}